The Golden Bear and both winners of the acting awards from this year's Berlinale, the director's award and the jury award from Cannes and much more will present the 6th year of the festival film from Berlin, Venice and Cannes. This year too, the Be2Can festival will bring a selection of the most remarkable and thought-provoking that the competitions of the three most important European film festivals have presented.
