Appendix 13 / Content of the work contract
1. Expressions starting with capital letters / All words and phrases that start with capital letters, the meaning of which is not determined by this contract for the work (hereinafter referred to as the "Agreement"), have the same meaning as in the contract, on the provision of services to support the operation and development of the information system - Service level agreement, the subject of which is the maintenance and development of the Application (hereinafter referred to as the "SLA").
