"He wrapped the animal in duct tape and rope and largely eliminated its vocalization. He put the dog in a jute bag, which he tied. Then they took the animal together to the river, where they threw it in the bag. At the moment when the dog was thrown into the water, the dog was demonstrably alive." said Zlín police spokeswoman Monika Kozumplíková.
