An exhibition of documents entitled Ad mandatum domini Regis: From the royal office and library of Wenceslas IV. prepared by the library together with the National Archives. On a written legacy from the reign of Wenceslas IV. the National Archives looks at it from the point of view of official documents and the National Library from the point of view of literary works, its author Jan Vojtíšek said about the exhibition.
