Hradec Králové should not even look back at last year's balance with Sparta. They lost in three out of four matches, taking points only once after the victory in Prague after extra time. In addition, Sparta's management brought several significant reinforcements in the summer and expects the team to return to the top.
"Sparta always had quality players, but what are we talking about, this year they are really loaded," admits Nedomlel before the first match later this week.
And the other one? Also a nice shift, waiting for Mountfield on Sunday afternoon in Třinec.
