Who doesn't know that the national treasure Lucie Bílá (53) is a seamstress by profession and her real name is Hana Zaňáková probably doesn't live in the Czech Republic. But the singer herself has now revealed that she almost worked in a glass factory!
Lucie Bílá knew from a relatively early age that she wanted to be a singer. Her love of singing was born when, as a little girl, she performed in the cultural center in her native Otvovice, where the warbler still lives.
